t: Amazon.com: G & S Metal Products Company
s: G&S Metal Products Company was founded in 1949, G&S Metal Products has been a family-owned, American producer of metal bakeware and kitchen products. many exceptional bakeware brands fall under G&S, such as OvenStuff, EZ Baker, ProBake, Baker Eze and Grill Sensations.

Since 1949, G&S has grown to become the largest producer of metal bakeware in the United States. G&S manufactures a superior product line of bakeware pans and distributes kitchen gadgets and accessories from all over the world at highly competitive prices.
